Class HDBManager

java.lang.Object
model.abstracts.AUser
model.User
model.HDBManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
IUserManagement
public class HDBManager extends User
Class representing an HDB Manager in the BTO Management System. Extends the User class directly, representing a distinct role from HDBOfficer.
